metadata.name: CUBES BURN
metadata.description:
Fifth Movement  
We stand at the steps of mystery. Looking up at the monolithic splendor before us. The light of a thousand stars pours out from the rotating object. Its shape, made up of several others, feels both infinite yet contained. How will it evolve? What gravity does it hold? How do we define an object that is ever-changing. For now, we embrace the paradox, and step open towards the light. 

CUBES BURN is a dynamic NFT. Built as an ever-changing soundscape, listen in as the journey unfolds throughout time. A new visual cue will let you know when the NFT has entered the next chapter. 

These tracks were composed to create an additional dimension during the viewing of [A Cube by Pak](https://opensea.io/collection/the-fungible-by-pak). For those willing to burn their Cubes, play this track to create an experiential ceremony as your NFT is converted into âœ– $ASH âœ–.
